### Gerar presigned URL
POST http://localhost:8080/uploads/presign
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "filename": "capa-frontal.jpg",
  "contentType": "image/jpeg"
}

### Gerar batch de presigned URLs
POST http://localhost:8080/uploads/presign-batch
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

[
  { "filename": "capa.jpg", "contentType": "image/jpeg" },
  { "filename": "lombada.jpg", "contentType": "image/jpeg" },
  { "filename": "detalhe.png", "contentType": "image/png" }
]

### Content type invalido (deve retornar 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/uploads/presign
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "filename": "arquivo.gif",
  "contentType": "image/gif"
}

### Sem auth (deve retornar 401)
POST http://localhost:8080/uploads/presign
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "filename": "capa.jpg",
  "contentType": "image/jpeg"
}
